data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful, quiet, ranch-style nestled in a friendly neighborhood. This home may be near the city, but with the spacious backyard and the dead-end street, this is your private nature oasis. Entertain with ease on the patio in this fully fenced, private backyard. This 3 bed, 1 bath home has a lot to offer with an open layout throughout. The main floor has been freshly painted and updated. The basement is full, and open. A great space for recreational use or creating your own private entertainment area.  The garage has been converted into a business workspace and is therefore extra livable space. It can still be used as a garage, great for those Michigan winters, or can be used as recreational or bonus space!
Beautifully maintained and well loved home just waiting for you!
